      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(memory): honor qmd search timeout for memory_search",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nFixes the outer memory_search tool deadline for QMD-backed memory search.\n\nThe memory_search tool had a hardcoded 15s deadline. For QMD-backed memory, this could fire before the configured QMD search timeout, which made slow local/self-hosted QMD setups fail even when memory.qmd.limits.timeoutMs was raised.\n\nThis change keeps 15s as the default minimum, but allows QMD-backed memory_search calls to honor a higher existing memory.qmd.limits.timeoutMs value.\n\n## Why\n\nsync.embeddingBatchTimeoutSeconds controls inline embedding batches during indexing. It does not control the interactive memory_search tool deadline.\n\nmemory.qmd.limits.timeoutMs is already the documented QMD search timeout, so the outer memory_search deadline should not be lower than it.\n\n## Tests\n\n- pnpm vitest extensions/memory-core/src/tools.test.ts --run",
        "branch": "fix/memory-search-timeout-config",
